40:56.060 --> 40:59.020
we as a desktop are not yet ready

40:59.020 --> 41:02.260
to fully replace either Windows or Mac OS still.

41:02.260 --> 41:03.940
And we covered this a little bit last week.

41:03.940 --> 41:06.600
